{"title":"黄河","authors":["商泽军　耿立"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":1,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商泽军　耿立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在远方的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看不懂我的黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在古版的典籍上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看不懂我的黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听到背纤人晚归的号子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还以为是逆水而上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样你也看不懂我的黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只有走着去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤脚走着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从入海口爬到中国的左上角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倚着高山倚着高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象着旋转的谷穗和炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象着有孩子和牛的村落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象着像雪一样的窗户纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂苞谷挂红薯秧的屋檐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象着微笑的夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安塞腰鼓走出窑洞涉过河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象着红高粱白糯米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象着上弦月勾着下弦月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后跪下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掬饮黄河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让沉重的黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从指缝撒落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样，你就看懂了我的黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就可以转过身去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着南方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一篇诗史慢慢地叙说＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}